comments: Gordon (HOU) ends his dribble and hops consecutively on the same foot after his gather.
Wood (HOU) makes marginal contact to LaVine's (CHI) front during his shooting motion and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Oladipo (HOU) at the end of his drive. Any arm contact after the dislodge is deemed incidental.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact with the ball, which then goes off of Oladipo's (HOU) hand and out of bounds.
LaVine (CHI) releases from Wood (HOU) at the end of his drive.
Markkanen (CHI) does not maintain verticality as he swipes down and makes contact with Wood's (HOU) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Wood (HOU) makes marginal contact with Young (CHI) as he attempts to roll towards the basket during the pick.
Tucker (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of LaVine (CHI) and absorbs the contact.
Tate (HOU) makes incidental contact to Markkanen's (CHI) arm during the rebound.
Oladipo (HOU) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
Tucker (HOU) makes contact to Temple's (CHI) arm that affects his SQBR.
Wood (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of LaVine (CHI) and absorbs the contact.
Temple (CHI) slightly extends his leg into Gordon's (HOU) path at the start of his drive, but the contact is marginal.
Gordon (HOU) briefly places two hands to Temple's (CHI) front off-ball and does not affect his FOM.
Oladipo (HOU) commits a take foul on Markkanen (CHI).
White (CHI) makes incidental contact with Oladipo (HOU) as both players come together prior to the inbounds pass.
Tate (HOU) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact to Gordon's (HOU) body during his shooting motion and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
